15F.207 Baseball and softball complex sales tax rebate. Repealed by its own terms;

2016 Acts, ch 1117, §1

2020 repeal takes effect 30 days following the date on which five million dollars in total rebates have been awarded; Code editor notified by economic development authority that the economic development authority board made its second sales tax rebate award, for a total of five million dollars in total rebates awarded, on December 12, 2018;

